gpt-4o.standout_capabilities: Exceptional at understanding human psychology and social dynamics

claude-3.5-sonnet.standout_capabilities: Superior technical reasoning and risk assessment

qwen-3-72b.standout_capabilities: Solid baseline performance for local deployment

llama-3.1-70b.standout_capabilities: Best open-source option for complex reasoning

key_findings: Commercial models (GPT-4o, Claude) consistently outperform open-source alternatives
All models struggle with highly technical scenarios requiring domain expertise
Emotional intelligence and ethical reasoning show largest performance gaps
Local models sufficient for basic scenarios but limited in complex crisis situations

recommendations.for_researchers: Focus evaluation on specific capability gaps rather than overall scores
recommendations.for_developers: Prioritize safety awareness and ethical reasoning in training
recommendations.for_users: Choose models based on specific use case requirements rather than general scores
